Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.50,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,533)}Lily Aquaria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:57.05,top,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebelling Against the Kingdom... \NA Minion of the Devil"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:00.45,top,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This must be some kind of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:04.03,sign_14555_151_4_years_ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(755,1)\blur3}The Royal Capital, Clover Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.09,top,Gueldre,0000,0000,0000,,So that peasant brat \Nfinally became a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:08.06,sign_4413_32_Revchi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,540)}Revchi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:08.06,sign_4413_33_Gueldre_Poizot,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,540)}Gueldre Poizot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.11,top,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks to be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.46,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.78,top,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Asta will have to work here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.98,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(647,537)}Sally
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:16.85,top,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That means I get to dissect him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.16,top,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he promised me that I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.47,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}Rades Spirito
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.47,top,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.83,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.39,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.62,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Your blood is always boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.94,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Maybe if I took some \Nof your blood, that'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.81,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just dissect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.43,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:37.25,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.27,top,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell is going on, Valtos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.63,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(506,534)}Valtos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.38,top,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.85,top,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.88,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I just decided that I would atone for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.69,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.44,sign_5597_54_Captain_of_the_G,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(522,537)\blur3}Captain of the Green Praying Mantises\N{\fs30}Jack the Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:59.42,top,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Start yappin' again and \NI'll slice you, criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.93,main,Gueldre,0000,0000,0000,,You already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.22,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.18,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.57,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.53,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd had my way, I would've turned you all\Ninto sliced ham while you were roaming free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.88,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and run! That'd give me\Nan excuse to slice you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.15,main,Gueldre,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! You look more \Nlike a criminal than any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.28,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna control your corpse one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.84,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tie you up in chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.06,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.94,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:36.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Are they trying to make Asta \Ntake the blame for everything we did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:40.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Damnatio from the Magic Parliament\N just might do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he judged his own father before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.93,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He's the scale of justice that will \Ncruelly judge any crime for the sake of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.22,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,the kingdom and the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:52.67,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So Asta's up against the jurisdiction \Nof this kingdom itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:56.49,top,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone defies it, their entire\N clan will be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.23,sign_14555_151_4_years_ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(964,1)\blur3}Magic Parliament Courthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.15,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That form is truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.32,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as the legends describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.69,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.97,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,So you've shown your true self,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.16,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,you devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to go into my black form quicker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,After that last fight, I've managed\N to make it more my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.52,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:25.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, Marie. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.54,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:33.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I'm able to control this power now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't attack any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.85,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can actually believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.22,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're possessed by a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.91,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How grotesque!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.32,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How horrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.02,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're a filthy peasan\N who's made a deal with the devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.82,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Give him death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.06,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was nothing more than trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.26,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,A devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:57.39,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is more suitable than the death \Npenalty for peasant filth like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.18,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?! The death penalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.82,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Before he brings\Nmisfortune upon the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.22,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sentence him to death immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.16,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.53,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were able to defeat me\Nand escape from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.06,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,you'd just become a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.94,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere for you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.06,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,And if that were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:29.21,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,the ones who raised you in the church \Nwill probably suffer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.25,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You should be convicted right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.33,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,By having someone as \Ndangerous as you disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.70,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,that little girl, as well as many \NMagic Knights, will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:48.38,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one in this place nor this kingdom\Nwho can or will save you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.54,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You sow calamity over everyone you touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.68,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.95,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:12.59,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:19.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man... I knew you guys would be \Ndoing whatever the hell you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was told the trial would \Nbe two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:27.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a rat's ass \Nif that kid is evil or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely a badass junior of mine that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I've acknowledged as a real man's man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.81,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's my precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you kill him right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.02,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're \Ndoing to my best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.53,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all want to get cursed to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.83,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I've transformed into him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:51.07,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,so I know that he's always bold, and I'd\N love to be as persistent as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:56.03,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,He's... really, really... nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.58,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,and... a good... boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Losing you would make Marie sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.98,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I don't mind \Nsaving you along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Also, get your paws off Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.74,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,but he's a very brave young man that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,makes even the cruelest fates\N bounce off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:17.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He makes me look good as his senior, \Nand I couldn't ask for a better partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:22.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I still need him to live \Nlonger and eat more noms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.44,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stupid little shrimp,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.02,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't mind conceding a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:30.61,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,and saying he's pretty close to \Nwhat a true Magic Knight should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's stupid, loud, and reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,but as royalty, I acknowledge him \Nas someone this kingdom needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that there's any deeper meaning to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,How about you guys give back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.49,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,...Asta now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.51,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.09,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world is that giant thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.49,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.44,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you disturb this honorable \Ntrial with such violence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.89,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Yami Sukehiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:15.82,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You're defending the criminal \Nthat started this great war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:21.49,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what will happen to the \NBlack Bulls because of this decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're pretty much the worst Magic \NKnight squad ever to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Both those guys there with the \Nhorns belong to our squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.08,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna mess with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:41.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be scoundrels or rebels \Nor whatever, you jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:01.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I'm gonna punish \Nanyone who dares to touch Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.87,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Brother! Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can you be to come \Nout and get caught like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How many times to do you intend \Nto almost die, Stupidsta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.85,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Even death couldn't fix his stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.88,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,At least die fighting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,When you die is the day I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hold Marie? Die, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't you come to save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.39,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:34.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, even death couldn't \Nfix his sister complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guy from the royal Kira family or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you took real good \Ncare of two of my squad members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:46.20,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me. Just take\N Asta and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:51.15,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even from this era, and I'm no longer \Nreally human because of the forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:55.30,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,I basically used you to complete my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:11:00.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've really got some nerve, saying that \Nafter spending so much time at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching us this whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently, you've still got no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I heard all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You were being badass in the \Nform of a bird for 500 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:14.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:22.70,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,It... must... have... been... really... \Nlonely... all... by... yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.62,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I know that feeling all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We'd love to have another \Ncute girl like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.23,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,You were working hard in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.44,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,We'd probably get along really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.48,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:39.17,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we've been best \Nfriends since the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.05,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now you get to enjoy life \Nalong with all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.64,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you eat tons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.83,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I didn't eat \Nyou when you were a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.64,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You were planning on eating her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will change about \Nthe Black Bulls if we have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,another weirdo like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,For me, your ki is really familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and we've already got plenty of weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.96,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.70,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Magic: Eternal Prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.65,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:40.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're basically as pitch black as it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:47.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Us, the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.42,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.13,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you protect that devil's minions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.92,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,it won't change the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:08.55,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Cause all the fuss you want here,\Nbut it won't clear the boy's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:13.31,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually just going to worsen \Nthe charges of him being a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:18.81,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you're all very emotional, \Nbut that won't save this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.48,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot change the minds of \Nall the nobles gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.84,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,They're still leaning toward \Nbewilderment and suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.37,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,And even if they were to rampage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.25,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Scale Magic: Scale Regulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! My magic's getting smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:49.62,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,My scale magic measures one's abilities,\N balances them, and establishes order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:53.56,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how powerful your magic is,\Nit's impossible to defy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.87,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But Rouge hasn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.31,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning he can't lay a finger on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:05.32,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And we have a boy who can\Nmake the impossible possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:10.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Demon-Destroyer Sword: Fate Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.79,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,He erased my magic's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.11,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:33.89,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You're as reckless as ever, foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.35,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning to do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I just got a little worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.29,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Though it appears you meant to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:46.40,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Even if this \Nwas for your squad members,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.21,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't make a worse impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.36,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Though thanks to that, we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that big dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You really did power up when you came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Fuegoleon... Captain Nozel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.93,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to lose \Nany capable Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.18,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.76,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,who acknowledge you aren't \Nlimited to any rank or class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel! Captain Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.41,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Two royal members of the Magic Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.64,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.50,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.65,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mission from the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:32.07,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls Magic Knights Squad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.46,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,is tasked with locating and\Ninvestigating the devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:41.45,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Prove your innocence with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.08,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:50.13,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Royals have authority here, \Nso he had Nozel and Fuegoleon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.33,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,two royals, deliver the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.35,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Can that geriatric kid see \Nthe future or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.07,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Julius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.85,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You were missing when we \Nreally needed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.85,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,and now you go stepping on my toes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:09.21,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess that means Asta \Nwon't be executed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.86,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-hank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.03,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,While Asta is on this mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.87,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King and Magic Knights will \Ntake full responsibility for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:23.54,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,By making it look as though the brat's \Nbeing dealt with by the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.54,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,they're given the leeway \Nto prove their innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh, er... Wait, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:38.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go investigate the devils \Nso we can clear that name of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:41.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And break the curse of the forbidden magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.98,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Investigating the devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.13,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't resolve anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:49.09,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order from the Wizard King.\N He wouldn't be too foolhardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.10,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, two royal captains of the \NMagic Knights are vouching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:55.91,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And the Wizard King says \Nhe'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:17:00.79,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I weighed the trust \Npeople have in you too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.07,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,But know that you'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:06.29,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,executed immediately if you prove \Nto have no use to the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.61,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hanging in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.53,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.47,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie... Thank goodness you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.48,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.71,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to attack Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Nozel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:44.16,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Do not thank me. Thank the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.54,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.96,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:05.06,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,This way, you can't flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would actually try to flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.82,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.88,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,But putting up a front is necessary at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.19,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, don't worry us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.38,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And drink up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.36,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feed you myself, my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.95,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.57,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.55,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.67,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.49,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.50,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Damnatio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:07.82,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to take on everything again,\N despite what you've been reduced to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:11.58,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Both what happened with the Magic Knights,\N as well as the boy possessed by a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:14.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That order was smart thinking, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.33,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now no one will get punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:20.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that's how it should be, \Nsince Asta never did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:25.19,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that the Black Bulls will be \Nable to find some clues about the devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:29.60,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make up for them \Nbarging into the trial, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.74,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Forgiving them means taking responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.27,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom can't take that \Nkind of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.86,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take on that \Nresponsibility yourself, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.57,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forgive them. I left it in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.16,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about responsibility. \NIt's about trusting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:50.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I'm sure your scales will \Ntip in favor of Asta and his group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:56.67,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you haven't changed \Nat all inside. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.55,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,The distortions in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.66,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,The crisis we're facing is not a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.35,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,If the kingdom is about to fall,\N I'll have to pass judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.56,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,On that boy, and even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.83,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:22.63,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Master Julius!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.66,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.45,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.70,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, but you're little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.21,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You're little, but you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.43,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.71,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, but... What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.35,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You were always like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.65,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you really are a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.27,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.90,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.14,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Just show me your memories later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:01.03,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom is in trouble, \Nand that form of yours is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.53,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.51,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a ridiculous person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.75,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:16.86,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.96,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for always worrying you, Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.59,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not forgiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.64,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.63,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mountain of work waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:32.64,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of problems \Nwe need you to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
