Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:07.65,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:12.03,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}There's Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:10.67,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,There's Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.49,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Theresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:18.04,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.50,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble. Here, look at today's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:25.00,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,All you people just keep saying, "This is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:37.01,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is... {\i1}what{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Nice, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, five hundred years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the tragedy between the humans \Nand the elves happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.90,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And it was all caused by a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:54.03,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 123:\N "Nero Reminisces... Part One."
